         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Private ¶ 14/2/87 ¶  ¶ Nothing has been further from my intention, dear Dr Ramsay, then that your own private resources should be taxed for the furtherance also of botanic science during Mr Bevan's Ex...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">87.02.14</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Edward Ramsay</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">ML MSS.562, Mitchell Library, State Library of New South Wales, Sydney.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Private</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">14/2/87</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Nothing has been further from my intention, dear Dr Ramsay, then that your own private resources should be taxed for the furtherance also of botanic science during Mr Bevan's Expedition.<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to E. Ramsay, 10 February 1887.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>My own position in this affair is perhaps not quite clear to you; it is this.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Our finance-year commences 1 July; the estimates are framed about May. Therefore even if the votes of the estimates are anticipated, it could be only in the new finance-year, that funds became available, and I am without any private means to make advances beyond the current incidental expenses of the Department.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>When the estimates are framed the heads of the public service here are always requested, to keep — if possible — within the votes of the last year; hence I should not be able, to make out a strong cause, <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">why</hi>
               </seg> an <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">extra</hi>
               </seg>-sum should be placed on the estimates for bot collections from New Guinea purposely the Vict. Gov. spending already £5000 <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">annually</hi>
               </seg> for the protectorate.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I certainly have a small annual vote hitherto regularly for purchase of plants and for an <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">occasional</hi>
               </seg> collector. This is by Bäuerlens travel for some months on the S. borders of N.SW., and by some aid to ascend the Bellenden Ker Mt,<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Qld.</p>
               </note> given to Sayers, quite exhausted for 1886; indeed I made a private monetary advance to the latter.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[…]<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Unknown amount of text missing.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </div>
